{"tid":1997877,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"講下你做過嘅Part time","createTime":"2020-05-02T03:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T04:43:12.000Z","uid":355018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8d754f9d00e6ba4d4b9729a4ed29de8fc16ad654","tid":1997877,"uid":355018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:54:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">分享下入職要求、福利、人工、伏位、行外唔知嘅事</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想轉工！<br />\n我先 而家係Uniqlo做緊<br />\n入職要求唔高，只要你個樣正正常常，冇鼻環、明顯誇張紋身嗰啲，正常溝通能力就多數請，不過都要睇season，3-6月淡季就冇回音㗎喇<br />\n人工65/h，辛苦嘅！摺衫、cleaning、出貨、散貨、轉layout、cashier、customer service乜都要做，冇停手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nstaff discount 30%off，減/特價品都可以再折，不過返工前要先洗錢...... btw pt仔真係唔清楚啲衫幾時減價 唔好再過嚟問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n伏位：日資公司要求多多，背守則、銷售目標...，乜都執正做，遇到hea嘅同事仲要幫佢執屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nU記好重視CS，寧願收少錢都唔想找少咗錢比個客<br />\n仲要唔可以gel甲、染淺色頭髮、著短褲、過膝裙翻工"},{"pid":"e3eda550e3ed0c4dc7860e4697527440779f11f9","tid":1997877,"uid":167295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"兒子"},{"pid":"63e2ca81fcf957309882e3e635c0e03a54a29218","tid":1997877,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3eda550e3ed0c4dc7860e4697527440779f11f9","tid":1997877,"uid":167295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"兒子"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:57:16.000Z","msg":"full time嚟"},{"pid":"b32a32faf93583f75534292c17431d441b6f2734","tid":1997877,"uid":149877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T04:03:22.000Z","msg":"上年返屈記<br />\n<br />\n基本上係睇返邊間鋪<br />\n<br />\n旺鋪極度chur 雖然人工